metadata.name: The Secret Turtle Society
metadata.description: The Secret Turtle Society is 8,888 art pieces carefully designed by the artist. A unique digital collection of diverse NFTs lying on Ethereum Blockchain. Each one is thoughtfully designed, specifically picked, and impeccably shaped. Join us on our adventure and have a good time. Having an NFT from our collection grants you creative and commercial rights, as well as inclusion in the community. Future perks can be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation.
